  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/18a9fdde8d0ab32ef46b482e8dbf65de.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>Got a bone to pick with someone?<br>Our new Trick-or-Yeet Update introduces Player vs Player action to the world of Karpathia. Crash, club, and kick your friends across 9 new maps and 3 different game modes including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>DEATHMATCH</li></ul> - A classic game mode where players will use a multitude of items, skills, and attacks to take down opponents either in teams or free-for-all gameplay!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>SPORTSBALL</li></ul> - In this basketball-a-like, two teams will compete and try to kick, throw, or dunk the ball into their opponent's hoop to score points. Guide your warriors to glory and bring the heat!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CAPTURE THE CHICKEN</li></ul> - Two teams attempt to steal the chicken and return it to their coop. Watch out for the fire traps or your chicken is cooked!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/709368e8173d6a91519675fcaf43b0c0.poster.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/709368e8173d6a91519675fcaf43b0c0.webm?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/709368e8173d6a91519675fcaf43b0c0.mp4?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to the crumbling world of Karpathia where humans are the endangered species. Only the Yeoman Eldritch Extermination Team can protect humanity against the hordes of chaos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/1a86e7b1fc5f0b51043912736d8461b4.poster.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/1a86e7b1fc5f0b51043912736d8461b4.webm?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/1a86e7b1fc5f0b51043912736d8461b4.mp4?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight battles solo or with friends locally and online (Beta) in this frantic gothic butt brawler, platform-brawling, co-op adventure for 1-4 players. Experience fast paced tactical combat as you battle a host of enemies, minibosses and giant bosses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8874bb16143364f4894b1ae40eb17e14.poster.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8874bb16143364f4894b1ae40eb17e14.webm?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8874bb16143364f4894b1ae40eb17e14.mp4?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>12 playable diverse gothic heroes to find, recruit and upgrade. Unlock and collect an array of usable scrolls, potions, weapons, traps, staffs, grenade bags and many other items. Pick up, aim and kick everything you can lay your hands on - stunned foes, skulls, brains, rocks, cabbages or even friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8e79fd560262b5d492b02d97ecac32e4.poster.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8e79fd560262b5d492b02d97ecac32e4.webm?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8e79fd560262b5d492b02d97ecac32e4.mp4?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>17 hand-crafted non-linear levels to explore across 3 vast regions. Lush, hand-painted artwork complemented by glossy VFX depicts an atmospheric world of ghosts, demons and ghouls that chills and charms.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/18a9fdde8d0ab32ef46b482e8dbf65de.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 /></span><br><br>Got a bone to pick with someone?<br>Our new Trick-or-Yeet Update introduces Player vs Player action to the world of Karpathia. Crash, club, and kick your friends across 9 new maps and 3 different game modes including:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>DEATHMATCH</li></ul> - A classic game mode where players will use a multitude of items, skills, and attacks to take down opponents either in teams or free-for-all gameplay!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>SPORTSBALL</li></ul> - In this basketball-a-like, two teams will compete and try to kick, throw, or dunk the ball into their opponent's hoop to score points. Guide your warriors to glory and bring the heat!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>CAPTURE THE CHICKEN</li></ul> - Two teams attempt to steal the chicken and return it to their coop. Watch out for the fire traps or your chicken is cooked!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/709368e8173d6a91519675fcaf43b0c0.poster.avif?t=1761340662\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/709368e8173d6a91519675fcaf43b0c0.webm?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/709368e8173d6a91519675fcaf43b0c0.mp4?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to the crumbling world of Karpathia where humans are the endangered species. Only the Yeoman Eldritch Extermination Team can protect humanity against the hordes of chaos.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline p