 src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8e79fd560262b5d492b02d97ecac32e4.webm?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1145330/extras/8e79fd560262b5d492b02d97ecac32e4.mp4?t=1761340662\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>17 hand-crafted non-linear levels to explore across 3 vast regions. Lush, hand-painted artwork complemented by glossy VFX depicts an atmospheric world of ghosts, demons and ghouls that chills and charms.",
